1
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:26,900
[A Splendid Match]

2
00:01:27,530 --> 00:01:29,620
[Episode 21]

3
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,280
Old Madam Wang

4
00:01:48,289 --> 00:01:51,360
[Old Madam Wang, Grandmother of Wang Zan]

5
00:01:49,870 --> 00:01:51,070
has been

6
00:01:51,070 --> 00:01:52,789
my close friend for years.

7
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,509
Dear sis,

8
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:56,720
these are

9
00:01:56,789 --> 00:01:58,250
my three granddaughters.

10
00:01:58,509 --> 00:02:00,480
Greetings, Madam Wang.

11
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:02,060
Please rise at once.

12
00:02:02,230 --> 00:02:03,670
You're truly blessed.

13
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:04,800
All your granddaughters

14
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:06,630
are breathtakingly beautiful.

15
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,280
Indeed.

16
00:02:08,150 --> 00:02:08,800
Zan,

17
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:11,360
bring the gifts we prepared.

18
00:02:11,430 --> 00:02:11,960
Alright.

19
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:15,280
Zhao.

20
00:02:19,079 --> 00:02:20,210
Thank you, Mr. Wang.

21
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:23,000
No need for such formalities.

22
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,630
Just call me Zan from now on.

23
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,440
Well then?

24
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:32,510
You can't get away from me now.

25
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,060
Zhao,

26
00:02:43,310 --> 00:02:44,370
mind your manners.

27
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:48,220
Grandmother, I didn't mean it.

28
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,030
I only meant to tease him a little.

29
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:51,690
Please don't take it to heart.

30
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,800
Of course not.

31
00:02:55,030 --> 00:02:56,079
You kids

32
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:57,079
playing around

33
00:02:57,190 --> 00:02:58,790
only shows how close you are.

34
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,150
Alright.

35
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,320
I need a private chat

36
00:03:02,430 --> 00:03:03,660
with Madam Wang.

37
00:03:03,910 --> 00:03:04,630
As for you girls,

38
00:03:04,630 --> 00:03:06,430
no need to stand on ceremony here.

39
00:03:06,430 --> 00:03:07,150
Sis,

40
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,810
what bad luck today.

41
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,430
Xian is still at school

42
00:03:10,870 --> 00:03:12,400
and can't keep Zan company.

43
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:14,160
Here's an idea.

44
00:03:14,870 --> 00:03:15,560
Zhao,

45
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,240
you're the eldest sister.

46
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,840
Show Mr. Wang and the others

47
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:20,190
around the garden.

48
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,190
Treat our guest well.

49
00:03:22,350 --> 00:03:22,900
I will.

50
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:31,320
Your grandmother's on my side.

51
00:03:38,590 --> 00:03:39,280
So what now?

52
00:03:39,750 --> 00:03:41,090
We're at your mansion.

53
00:03:41,310 --> 00:03:42,770
Dare you lay a finger on me?

54
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:45,280
Lan,

55
00:03:45,430 --> 00:03:46,560
I just remembered

56
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:48,280
I still have embroidery to finish.

57
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:49,140
Help me with it.

58
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:50,840
Huh?

59
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:52,000
But…

60
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,460
Stop hesitating, come on.

61
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,120
See?

62
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,430
Even your own sister

63
00:03:58,430 --> 00:04:00,110
is trying to match us up.

64
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,400
Why are you still being so stubborn?

65
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,000
Weren't we going to tour the garden?

66
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,310
Why are you leading me to the gate?

67
00:04:13,310 --> 00:04:14,280
I'm sending you home.

68
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,030
I never said I'm leaving.

69
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:15,960
Stop right there!

70
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:16,720
Stop!

71
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,720
What are you up to?

72
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:20,390
You know exactly.

73
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,240
I even asked my grandmother

74
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,040
to come here

75
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,560
just to see you.

76
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,430
This is the Gu Mansion,

77
00:04:26,430 --> 00:04:27,510
not your Wang manor.

78
00:04:27,510 --> 00:04:29,440
Precisely because it's your home.

79
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:31,390
You're the host, I'm the guest.

80
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,270
If you slight me,

81
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,960
it'll make your whole family

82
00:04:35,070 --> 00:04:36,200
look discourteous.

83
00:04:36,950 --> 00:04:38,750
You're a young lady while I'm a gentleman.

84
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:39,880
If we make a scene,

85
00:04:40,070 --> 00:04:40,990
you'll be the one

86
00:04:40,990 --> 00:04:42,270
losing face in the end.

87
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:44,200
You have no shame at all.

88
00:04:45,310 --> 00:04:46,510
To tell you the truth,

89
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,060
ever since I was a child

90
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,430
this is just how I am.

91
00:04:49,750 --> 00:04:51,350
What can you even do about it?

92
00:04:53,510 --> 00:04:54,680
I have to admit

93
00:04:56,430 --> 00:04:57,680
you look quite lovely

94
00:04:57,830 --> 00:04:59,030
when you're annoyed.

95
00:04:59,310 --> 00:04:59,950
Exactly.

96
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,630
Just like this.

97
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:05,310
Such a charming angry beauty.

98
00:05:05,310 --> 00:05:06,430
Get away from me!

99
00:05:08,390 --> 00:05:09,870
Don't shy away.

100
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:11,190
Leave me alone!

101
00:05:20,630 --> 00:05:21,480
Gu Jinzhao.

102
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:24,290
Just you wait.

103
00:05:24,430 --> 00:05:25,040
I don't hold the silly rule

104
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,510
of never hitting a woman.

105
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:34,150
What's he doing here?

106
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,100
Mr. Wang,

107
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:39,820
how did you fall into the pond?

108
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:41,390
I'm so sorry.

109
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:42,630
Come out quickly.

110
00:05:42,630 --> 00:05:44,560
Don't get your clothes any wetter.

111
00:05:46,190 --> 00:05:47,070
Hurry up.

112
00:05:47,390 --> 00:05:48,720
Father's brought guests over.

113
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,130
What guests?

114
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,530
This way please.

115
00:05:54,630 --> 00:05:55,600
Chen Yanyun.

116
00:05:58,430 --> 00:05:59,720
Why is he here at your manor?

117
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,980
Our two families are old family friends.

118
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:03,830
Come on.

119
00:06:04,310 --> 00:06:06,970
Go to the guest courtyard.
I'll get you changed.

120
00:06:07,510 --> 00:06:09,310
Your mood shifts so fast.

121
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:10,630
Are you coming or not?

122
00:06:12,270 --> 00:06:12,830
Let's go.

123
00:06:17,070 --> 00:06:18,360
Isn't that Zhao?

124
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,190
Who's that soaked mess?

125
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:31,920
Why'd you stop?

126
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:37,510
You may head back.

127
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:38,710
I've got things to do.

128
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:39,750
Gu Jinzhao,

129
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:43,430
I've already told my family

130
00:06:43,630 --> 00:06:45,630
I'll marry only you.

131
00:06:46,190 --> 00:06:47,650
Have you lost your senses?

132
00:06:48,510 --> 00:06:49,480
Grandmother came today

133
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,870
to propose our marriage.

134
00:06:50,870 --> 00:06:52,130
You look down on me now,

135
00:06:52,510 --> 00:06:53,510
but once we're married,

136
00:06:53,510 --> 00:06:55,570
you'll have to stay by my side always.

137
00:06:56,190 --> 00:06:58,120
If I make you weep, you can't smile.

138
00:06:58,310 --> 00:06:59,440
If I tell you to live,

139
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:00,920
you dare not die.

140
00:07:00,950 --> 00:07:01,510
You…

141
00:07:07,410 --> 00:07:08,820
Is that all you've got?

142
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:20,450
If you dare marry me,

143
00:07:20,630 --> 00:07:22,160
I'll never let you off easy.

144
00:07:25,510 --> 00:07:26,360
It's all a misunderstanding.

145
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:26,960
Step back.

146
00:07:29,060 --> 00:07:30,780
Careful now.

147
00:07:30,860 --> 00:07:32,120
it's quite dangerous.

148
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:35,000
A misunderstanding.

149
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:36,020
Step back more.

150
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,040
Leave at once!

151
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:41,570
Get out!

152
00:07:51,940 --> 00:07:52,790
Miss Zhao,

153
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:54,510
Lord Chen has arrived at our manor.

154
00:07:54,510 --> 00:07:56,000
Master asks you to greet him

155
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,659
and help attend to the guests.

156
00:07:58,630 --> 00:07:59,360
Understood.

157
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,480
Wait a moment.

158
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:05,950
Why has Lord Chen

159
00:08:05,950 --> 00:08:07,360
come so unexpectedly?

160
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:09,310
Miss Zhao,

161
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:10,190
Lord Chen

162
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:11,870
was at the Ministry of Revenue
on official business.

163
00:08:11,870 --> 00:08:13,560
Our master went to report to him

164
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,560
and talked till office hours ended,

165
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:15,560
still unfinished.

166
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,390
So Master invited

167
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:18,040
Lord Chen over to our home.

168
00:08:18,190 --> 00:08:20,120
To our surprise, he agreed.

169
00:08:20,510 --> 00:08:21,360
Master is quite nervous

170
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,630
right now.

171
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:23,950
He's nervous,

172
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:26,210
yet sends me to deal with it?

173
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:28,920
Please don't be upset, Miss.

174
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,510
Master has no other choice.

175
00:08:30,830 --> 00:08:31,950
Lord Chen mentioned

176
00:08:31,950 --> 00:08:33,510
craving a dish we make

177
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:36,669
with sliced meat and mushrooms

178
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,630
but couldn't recall

179
00:08:37,630 --> 00:08:38,549
its name.

180
00:08:38,870 --> 00:08:40,030
That's why Master asks

181
00:08:40,030 --> 00:08:42,200
you to help prepare it.

182
00:08:44,390 --> 00:08:45,650
I know which dish it is.

183
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:47,750
It just came to me.

184
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:50,670
The men are chatting in the front hall.

185
00:08:50,670 --> 00:08:52,360
It's improper for me to go there.

186
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,360
Go tell Master

187
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:54,240
I'll head straight

188
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,720
to oversee the feast arrangements.

189
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:56,600
I won't go pay formal respects.

190
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:58,000
Miss, that's…

191
00:08:58,290 --> 00:08:59,550
Just tell him plainly.

192
00:08:59,670 --> 00:09:00,910
No one will blame you.

193
00:09:03,750 --> 00:09:04,390
Very well.

194
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,160
She really said that?

195
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:24,670
That stubborn girl

196
00:09:24,910 --> 00:09:26,370
has no regard for decency.

197
00:09:34,870 --> 00:09:35,600
My Lord,

198
00:09:36,340 --> 00:09:37,790
my daughter feels

199
00:09:37,810 --> 00:09:40,210
it inappropriate
to come to the front yard.

200
00:09:45,270 --> 00:09:47,200
She's always been rather reserved.

201
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:49,870
I'll send someone to fetch her at once.

202
00:09:51,970 --> 00:09:53,380
It's only a simple dish.

203
00:09:54,150 --> 00:09:55,870
No need to trouble your daughter

204
00:09:55,870 --> 00:09:56,930
to come over again.

205
00:09:57,560 --> 00:09:58,600
Yes, of course.

206
00:09:59,510 --> 00:10:01,270
Maybe let my daughter

207
00:10:01,270 --> 00:10:02,790
supervise the kitchen.

208
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:03,390
By the way,

209
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:04,240
what dishes do you prefer

210
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,770
or have any dietary taboos?

211
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,240
Your daughter

212
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:09,240
knows my tastes well.

213
00:10:13,190 --> 00:10:14,170
Naturally.

214
00:10:15,030 --> 00:10:15,870
Of course.

215
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,750
She should know.

216
00:10:23,280 --> 00:10:26,440
[Eternal Glory]

217
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,700
My deepest apologies.

218
00:10:25,270 --> 00:10:26,070
As you can see,

219
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,320
we never expected Lord Chen

220
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,790
to drop by so suddenly.

221
00:10:31,510 --> 00:10:33,090
It only shows

222
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:35,760
how close he is to your family.

223
00:10:35,870 --> 00:10:38,550
He's a Grand Secretary in court.

224
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,270
This is great news.

225
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:41,720
As for the marriage proposal,

226
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:42,970
I'll keep it in mind.

227
00:10:42,990 --> 00:10:44,340
Just wait for my reply.

228
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:46,000
That would be wonderful.

229
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:47,320
Please stop here.

230
00:10:48,810 --> 00:10:50,040
Second daughter-in-law,

231
00:10:50,040 --> 00:10:51,190
see our guest out.

232
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:52,670
Yes.

233
00:10:53,150 --> 00:10:54,120
Farewell.

234
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:56,150
After you.

235
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:57,200
Very well.

236
00:11:05,670 --> 00:11:06,150
Hurry,

237
00:11:06,550 --> 00:11:07,630
send a fast rider

238
00:11:07,750 --> 00:11:09,720
to fetch Second Master
from the official office,

239
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:11,120
tell him Lord Chen is here

240
00:11:11,230 --> 00:11:12,320
and ask him to come back right away.

241
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:12,870
OK.

242
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:17,970
Also find

243
00:11:18,150 --> 00:11:19,150
a trusted servant

244
00:11:19,510 --> 00:11:21,040
to the front hall to find out

245
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,200
the best moment

246
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:23,630
to meet Lord Chen.

247
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:24,810
Understood.

248
00:11:27,180 --> 00:11:30,470
[Eternal Glory]

249
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,440
Lord Chen.

250
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:47,960
Lord Gu.

251
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:50,380
It's an honor to have you here.

252
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:52,630
I regret not greeting you earlier.

253
00:11:52,630 --> 00:11:54,360
Please pardon my discourtesy.

254
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,380
No need for such formalities.

255
00:11:59,150 --> 00:11:59,870
Old Madam.

256
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:04,510
What did he say?

257
00:12:04,510 --> 00:12:05,200
Madam,

258
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,670
Second Master reports,

259
00:12:06,670 --> 00:12:08,080
Lord Chen gave special instructions

260
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,630
not to trouble the household elders,

261
00:12:09,630 --> 00:12:11,030
asking you and the madam

262
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:13,040
to skip the formal greeting.

263
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,440
How could he act so aloof?

264
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:19,750
Is he looking down on our family?

265
00:12:20,910 --> 00:12:22,520
Where will they dine?

266
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:24,410
In Fourth Master's quarters.

267
00:12:26,510 --> 00:12:27,960
I see. You may leave.

268
00:12:28,030 --> 00:12:28,550
Yes.

269
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,580
No wonder.

270
00:12:33,870 --> 00:12:34,620
It's definitely

271
00:12:34,620 --> 00:12:36,410
all because of the Ji family.

272
00:12:36,870 --> 00:12:39,200
Zhao is on close terms with Lord Chen.

273
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,750
Mom is far too lenient.

274
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,000
In my opinion,

275
00:12:44,020 --> 00:12:45,120
it's nothing more than master

276
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:46,120
and servant.

277
00:12:46,790 --> 00:12:47,360
Zhao

278
00:12:47,550 --> 00:12:49,360
is just going to wait on him.

279
00:12:49,510 --> 00:12:50,790
Don't talk nonsense!

280
00:12:51,630 --> 00:12:53,190
He's still in the mansion.

281
00:12:55,390 --> 00:12:56,150
Mother,

282
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:57,960
I think

283
00:12:58,080 --> 00:13:00,030
it's better we don't greet him.

284
00:13:00,030 --> 00:13:01,830
We rarely have contact with him.

285
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,450
A sudden formal visit

286
00:13:03,510 --> 00:13:05,360
might lead to a misstep in etiquette

287
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,490
and make us look bad.

288
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:10,320
That's exactly the point.

289
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,580
On normal days,

290
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:14,150
we have no dealings with him,

291
00:13:14,150 --> 00:13:15,810
yet he shows up out of nowhere.

292
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:18,120
He must have some hidden intent.

293
00:14:00,790 --> 00:14:01,790
This is too bland.

294
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,390
Third Master likes strong flavors,

295
00:14:03,390 --> 00:14:04,720
especially spicy food.

296
00:14:04,870 --> 00:14:05,870
Add more oil and salt

297
00:14:05,870 --> 00:14:07,000
to taste richer.

298
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,750
Make it five shades heavier

299
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,520
than our usual taste.

300
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,630
Five shades?

301
00:14:23,910 --> 00:14:25,960
My Lord, please.

302
00:14:27,030 --> 00:14:27,510
Good.

303
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:49,670
Not bad.

304
00:14:51,830 --> 00:14:53,230
You should all try it too.

305
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,210
Okay, okay.

306
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:54,750
Okay, My Lord.

307
00:14:54,750 --> 00:14:55,240
Good.

308
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:07,910
Good wine.

309
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:14,440
This is a twenty-year-old Sangluo wine.

310
00:15:14,510 --> 00:15:16,080
I'm glad you like it, My Lord.

311
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:16,790
Here.

312
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:19,300
Allow me to fill your cup, My Lord.

313
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:23,940
[Sangluo Wine]

314
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:29,750
Second Master asked to send two more jars

315
00:15:29,750 --> 00:15:31,950
of Sangluo wine to the front courtyard.

316
00:15:41,870 --> 00:15:43,270
He can drink this much?

317
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:45,320
My Lady,

318
00:15:45,910 --> 00:15:47,870
I'm afraid Third Master and the others
have had too salty food,

319
00:15:47,870 --> 00:15:49,600
and have to drown it in wine now.

320
00:15:54,910 --> 00:15:56,000
Put some more perilla

321
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,150
in this soup.

322
00:15:57,510 --> 00:15:58,200
Yes.

323
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:06,720
However,

324
00:16:06,870 --> 00:16:09,050
no matter how good the wine is,
one shouldn't drink too much.

325
00:16:09,050 --> 00:16:10,450
It's getting late today.

326
00:16:10,790 --> 00:16:11,480
Let's

327
00:16:12,030 --> 00:16:13,030
stop here for now.

328
00:16:13,150 --> 00:16:14,390
Yes, it is getting late.

329
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:14,870
My Lord,

330
00:16:15,030 --> 00:16:16,900
if you don't mind, how about

331
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:17,790
just staying over?

332
00:16:17,790 --> 00:16:19,650
You can go back tomorrow morning.

333
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:32,060
That works too.

334
00:16:32,910 --> 00:16:33,790
I'm just afraid

335
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:36,580
it might be inconvenient.

336
00:16:38,390 --> 00:16:39,390
It is convenient.

337
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:42,170
Nothing could be more convenient.

338
00:16:42,390 --> 00:16:43,790
Someone, hurry!

339
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:46,060
Go and get the guest courtyard...

340
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:46,750
No.

341
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:49,750
Clean up Cuizhu Residence.

342
00:16:49,790 --> 00:16:50,270
Yes.

343
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:52,240
It's quiet there.

344
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,750
Yes, My Lord.

345
00:16:56,870 --> 00:16:57,510
What?

346
00:16:57,870 --> 00:16:58,750
He stayed?

347
00:16:58,870 --> 00:16:59,600
Yes.

348
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:01,600
I heard he drank too much.

349
00:17:02,510 --> 00:17:03,840
He's really something.

350
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:06,510
Is he staying in the guest courtyard?

351
00:17:06,510 --> 00:17:07,880
I'm not sure.

352
00:17:08,510 --> 00:17:09,510
Probably.

353
00:17:18,349 --> 00:17:19,440
Qingpu, come here.

354
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:20,920
In a while,

355
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:22,310
sneak over to the guest courtyard,

356
00:17:22,310 --> 00:17:23,750
and check what he is doing.

357
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:25,720
I'll take a detour
around Cuizhu Residence,

358
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:27,180
to avoid running into him.

359
00:17:27,349 --> 00:17:28,640
My Lady, you...

360
00:17:31,350 --> 00:17:32,750
Why do you have to do this?

361
00:17:32,920 --> 00:17:34,880
Third Master clearly wants to see you.

362
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:36,310
And you want to see Third Master too.

363
00:17:36,310 --> 00:17:38,170
Just go quickly when I tell you to.

364
00:17:50,830 --> 00:17:52,760
I can't believe this Chen Yanyun.

365
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,640
It's his first time at our mansion.

366
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:55,590
Why didn't he think of

367
00:17:55,590 --> 00:17:57,250
coming to pay respects to me?

368
00:17:57,790 --> 00:17:59,040
Mother,

369
00:17:59,510 --> 00:18:01,590
he is a dignified Grand Secretary.

370
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:03,550
The fact that he's willing
to visit our mansion

371
00:18:03,550 --> 00:18:05,080
is already giving us honor.

372
00:18:06,030 --> 00:18:07,490
I really didn't expect it.

373
00:18:08,110 --> 00:18:10,510
My sister-in-law has already passed away.

374
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:12,130
How could the Fourth

375
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:14,830
still connect with Chen?

376
00:18:17,110 --> 00:18:19,270
Thinking back on it now,

377
00:18:20,110 --> 00:18:21,960
right after my sister-in-law passed away,

378
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:24,090
so many imperial censors impeached him.

379
00:18:24,090 --> 00:18:25,270
If it were anyone else,

380
00:18:25,270 --> 00:18:26,600
this official position

381
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:29,070
would definitely have been lost.

382
00:18:29,790 --> 00:18:30,400
But

383
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:33,580
the Fourth unexpectedly remained unscathed

384
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:36,740
and continued as a Director
in the Ministry of Revenue.

385
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:39,280
Now that I think about it,

386
00:18:39,750 --> 00:18:40,550
most likely,

387
00:18:40,550 --> 00:18:42,510
this Chen Yanyun was helping him.

388
00:18:44,480 --> 00:18:46,880
But what virtue or ability
does the Fourth have

389
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:48,070
to make Chen

390
00:18:48,310 --> 00:18:50,510
look upon him with such favor?

391
00:18:51,510 --> 00:18:53,070
I don't know either.

392
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:55,920
Earlier, Chen drank too much.

393
00:18:56,070 --> 00:18:56,790
I thought

394
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:58,920
we should escort him back properly.

395
00:18:59,510 --> 00:19:02,200
But the Fourth actually asked Lord Chen

396
00:19:02,640 --> 00:19:04,960
if he wanted to just stay over.

397
00:19:05,440 --> 00:19:07,270
I was startled at the time.

398
00:19:07,920 --> 00:19:09,090
But the thing is,

399
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:10,510
Chen

400
00:19:10,720 --> 00:19:13,070
actually agreed.

401
00:19:15,270 --> 00:19:16,640
It seems

402
00:19:17,070 --> 00:19:18,200
in the future,

403
00:19:18,510 --> 00:19:21,310
we should treat the fourth branch better.

404
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:23,050
After this,

405
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:24,350
who knows,

406
00:19:25,070 --> 00:19:26,510
we might need his help.

407
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:28,510
Deyuan,

408
00:19:29,790 --> 00:19:30,790
you didn't take

409
00:19:30,790 --> 00:19:32,550
someone's money again, did you?

410
00:19:32,550 --> 00:19:33,440
No.

411
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:36,820
You must not act foolishly again.

412
00:19:37,790 --> 00:19:38,920
Have you forgotten?

413
00:19:39,070 --> 00:19:39,880
I haven't.

414
00:19:41,200 --> 00:19:41,800
That year,

415
00:19:42,110 --> 00:19:42,720
you took

416
00:19:42,720 --> 00:19:45,030
twenty thousand taels of silver
from the Vice Minister of Works.

417
00:19:45,030 --> 00:19:46,890
The next year he got into trouble.

418
00:19:47,310 --> 00:19:48,880
If I hadn't gone to Madam Ji

419
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:50,110
to borrow money to cover this deficit,

420
00:19:50,110 --> 00:19:51,790
-you...
-That's enough.

421
00:19:52,110 --> 00:19:52,920
Mother,

422
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:54,830
these are old, stale matters.

423
00:19:54,830 --> 00:19:56,510
Why bring them up?

424
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:57,880
I'm reminding you.

425
00:19:58,070 --> 00:19:59,830
An official must be honest and upright.

426
00:19:59,830 --> 00:20:02,760
If household expenses aren't enough,
I have my ways.

427
00:20:03,030 --> 00:20:03,960
Who is there?

428
00:20:04,790 --> 00:20:05,750
Come out quickly!

429
00:20:05,750 --> 00:20:06,310
Who is it?

430
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:07,880
Go check it.

431
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:33,160
Don't run!

432
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:34,750
I see you!

433
00:21:10,880 --> 00:21:11,510
Master.

434
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:15,960
I just came to check on your Lord.

435
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:17,920
If he needs anything,

436
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:20,300
I can order someone to bring it over.

437
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:25,130
Our Lord has already gone to sleep.

438
00:21:26,110 --> 00:21:26,720
Then,

439
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:29,160
I will take my leave.

440
00:21:51,590 --> 00:21:52,520
Are you alright?

441
00:21:56,350 --> 00:21:57,270
What happened?

442
00:21:57,550 --> 00:22:00,210
Why are they
making things so difficult for you?

443
00:22:01,830 --> 00:22:02,830
I heard some

444
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:05,060
private talk I shouldn't have heard.

445
00:22:05,550 --> 00:22:06,480
About Gu Deyuan?

446
00:22:13,350 --> 00:22:16,440
The position of Right Vice Minister
of Personnel is vacant.

447
00:22:16,440 --> 00:22:17,400
This is a good position.

448
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:18,860
Many people are eyeing it.

449
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:21,400
Your second uncle is one of them.

450
00:22:22,070 --> 00:22:23,270
He can get it?

451
00:22:24,070 --> 00:22:25,330
There's no hope at all.

452
00:22:28,110 --> 00:22:30,440
If he could just
know his place and lay low,

453
00:22:30,590 --> 00:22:31,720
and not be targeted,

454
00:22:32,440 --> 00:22:33,600
for the Gu family,

455
00:22:33,750 --> 00:22:35,610
it might actually be a good thing.

456
00:22:36,390 --> 00:22:38,590
There's a hidden meaning in your words.

457
00:22:39,030 --> 00:22:40,890
Let's not talk about him anymore.

458
00:22:42,440 --> 00:22:43,110
You...

459
00:22:43,880 --> 00:22:46,140
Shouldn't you be in the guest courtyard?

460
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:47,590
Why are you here?

461
00:22:50,830 --> 00:22:52,350
So you knew I stayed over.

462
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:55,720
I'm going back.

463
00:23:00,070 --> 00:23:01,600
We finally managed to meet.

464
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,930
Why are you in such a hurry to leave?

465
00:23:05,790 --> 00:23:06,240
Well, could I

466
00:23:06,240 --> 00:23:07,840
just stay here and not leave?

467
00:23:09,790 --> 00:23:11,320
I won't talk to you anymore.

468
00:23:13,510 --> 00:23:14,750
Is it because you saw me

469
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:16,410
that you were with that Wang,

470
00:23:16,510 --> 00:23:17,770
laughing and talking?

471
00:23:18,350 --> 00:23:19,350
Nonsense.

472
00:23:21,310 --> 00:23:22,550
He is a guest.

473
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:28,600
It's really too late.

474
00:23:29,160 --> 00:23:30,310
I have to go.

475
00:23:30,310 --> 00:23:32,350
I have already explained to my mentor.

476
00:23:32,350 --> 00:23:35,480
The marriage between me
and Xue Qinglan is called off.

477
00:23:36,470 --> 00:23:37,530
From now on, he

478
00:23:37,720 --> 00:23:39,980
won't act as a matchmaker for me anymore.

479
00:23:41,270 --> 00:23:41,830
Then,

480
00:23:42,350 --> 00:23:43,510
will the Chief Grand Secretary

481
00:23:43,510 --> 00:23:44,970
be dissatisfied with you?

482
00:23:45,240 --> 00:23:45,960
Perhaps.

483
00:23:46,590 --> 00:23:48,390
But I can't care about that much.

484
00:23:52,000 --> 00:23:53,460
Didn't I tell you already?

485
00:23:54,270 --> 00:23:55,270
Marrying you

486
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:56,680
brings no benefit to me.

487
00:23:58,440 --> 00:24:00,640
Then what if we set aside those factors?

488
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:03,690
Just speaking of you and me.

489
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:05,790
Are you willing

490
00:24:06,590 --> 00:24:07,550
to be with me?

491
00:24:20,350 --> 00:24:22,210
I know what you are worried about.

492
00:24:22,840 --> 00:24:23,590
But could you

493
00:24:23,590 --> 00:24:25,650
hold off on making a decision for now?

494
00:24:26,510 --> 00:24:27,590
When we encounter problems,

495
00:24:27,590 --> 00:24:29,050
let's not rush to retreat.

496
00:24:29,110 --> 00:24:30,110
Let's see if we can

497
00:24:30,640 --> 00:24:32,700
figure out a way to solve it together.

498
00:24:33,310 --> 00:24:34,070
Okay?

499
00:24:43,750 --> 00:24:44,480
Okay.

500
00:25:14,170 --> 00:25:17,170
♪ A good moment is strewn with starlight ♪

501
00:25:17,740 --> 00:25:21,370
♪ Flames burn away
the frost of bygone days ♪

502
00:25:22,250 --> 00:25:26,280
♪ Reflections tremble,
hearts beat in unison ♪

503
00:25:27,660 --> 00:25:30,820
♪ Candlelight weaves the web of fate ♪

504
00:25:32,080 --> 00:25:34,810
♪ Petal shadows
trace the lines of your face ♪

505
00:25:35,930 --> 00:25:39,490
♪ Fleeting light
sketches the shape of fate ♪

506
00:25:40,290 --> 00:25:44,010
♪ Steps are light,
but feelings are hard to hide ♪

507
00:25:44,770 --> 00:25:49,200
♪ In a backward glance,
a few hidden feelings slip through ♪

508
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:53,600
♪ Ask the passing time
whether it has forgotten ♪

509
00:25:54,410 --> 00:25:56,230
♪ The moonlight of our first encounter ♪

510
00:25:57,270 --> 00:26:00,930
♪ Year after year,
it etches your likeness ♪

511
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:04,240
♪ Count the faint shimmer
of the starry river ♪

512
00:26:05,120 --> 00:26:08,900
♪ Yet none compares
to the gentle light in your eyes ♪

513
00:26:09,600 --> 00:26:11,860
♪ At last, I see the galaxy
shimmering and swaying ♪

514
00:26:12,710 --> 00:26:14,470
♪ Reflected in our eyes ♪

515
00:26:15,340 --> 00:26:20,000
♪ I'll be with you forever ♪

516
00:26:21,150 --> 00:26:24,650
♪ And enjoy
the beautiful scenery with you ♪

517
00:26:26,940 --> 00:26:30,730
♪ For all the days of our lives,
our love will endure ♪

518
00:26:32,290 --> 00:26:34,560
♪ Ask the passing time
whether it has forgotten ♪

519
00:26:35,200 --> 00:26:36,900
♪ The moonlight of our first encounter ♪

520
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:41,580
♪ Year after year,
it etches your likeness ♪

521
00:26:42,370 --> 00:26:44,720
♪ Count the faint shimmer
of the starry river ♪

522
00:26:45,770 --> 00:26:49,550
♪ Yet none compares
to the gentle light in your eyes ♪

523
00:26:50,250 --> 00:26:52,510
♪ At last, I see the galaxy
shimmering and swaying ♪

524
00:26:53,360 --> 00:26:55,120
♪ Reflected in our eyes ♪

525
00:26:55,990 --> 00:27:00,650
♪ I'll be with you forever ♪

526
00:27:01,600 --> 00:27:03,590
♪ And enjoy
the beautiful scenery with you ♪

527
00:27:04,350 --> 00:27:05,750
Where is it?

528
00:27:11,880 --> 00:27:12,750
I remember earlier

529
00:27:12,750 --> 00:27:14,030
I dropped it right here.

530
00:27:14,030 --> 00:27:15,620
Why is it gone?

531
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:18,240
The earrings

532
00:27:18,260 --> 00:27:19,290
were from Wenxiu!

533
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:35,480
Wait a minute.

534
00:27:42,510 --> 00:27:44,510
Good thing it's not found by others.

535
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:55,000
About this,

536
00:27:55,510 --> 00:27:57,110
perhaps it's better if I step forward.

537
00:27:57,110 --> 00:27:57,830
No need.

538
00:27:58,310 --> 00:27:59,570
I can handle it myself.

539
00:28:01,920 --> 00:28:02,640
This way.

540
00:28:05,720 --> 00:28:07,000
My Lady!

541
00:28:07,510 --> 00:28:08,240
Look,

542
00:28:08,750 --> 00:28:10,030
isn't that Miss Gu?

543
00:28:14,550 --> 00:28:17,200
Why did she come out of Cuizhu Residence?

544
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:19,610
That's strange.

545
00:28:20,240 --> 00:28:22,110
Lord Chen is

546
00:28:22,110 --> 00:28:24,510
also staying at Cuizhu Residence tonight.

547
00:28:28,590 --> 00:28:30,030
I knew it!

548
00:28:30,550 --> 00:28:31,510
She is just a half-orphan
whose father doesn't care

549
00:28:31,510 --> 00:28:33,200
and who lost her mother.

550
00:28:33,310 --> 00:28:34,910
How could she be so arrogant?

551
00:28:35,070 --> 00:28:35,590
Also,

552
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:37,110
why would the Ji family

553
00:28:37,110 --> 00:28:38,680
hand over so many properties
in the capital

554
00:28:38,680 --> 00:28:39,200
to a

555
00:28:39,200 --> 00:28:40,600
girl who just came of age?

556
00:28:41,640 --> 00:28:42,160
Right!

557
00:28:44,270 --> 00:28:45,920
Chen even specially

558
00:28:45,920 --> 00:28:48,380
went to attend her coming-of-age ceremony.

559
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:51,510
Now it all makes sense.

560
00:28:51,830 --> 00:28:52,960
So,

561
00:28:53,720 --> 00:28:55,650
they have long had a secret affair.

562
00:28:56,960 --> 00:29:00,880
A secret rendezvous late at night
with a current Grand Secretary!

563
00:29:02,510 --> 00:29:04,590
Gu Jinzhao,

564
00:29:04,790 --> 00:29:06,250
you are really something.

565
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:13,610
[Generations of Excellence]

566
00:29:11,310 --> 00:29:11,920
My Lady,

567
00:29:12,110 --> 00:29:14,310
when is Third Master coming to propose?

568
00:29:15,160 --> 00:29:16,050
Propose?

569
00:29:16,110 --> 00:29:17,750
Third Master is always swift and decisive.

570
00:29:17,750 --> 00:29:18,680
It must be soon.

571
00:29:19,510 --> 00:29:20,640
What proposal?

572
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:22,110
I haven't completely decided

573
00:29:22,110 --> 00:29:23,040
to marry him yet.

574
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:25,510
You still haven't decided?

575
00:29:25,830 --> 00:29:26,440
You two...

576
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:28,440
Haven't you already...

577
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:32,350
Yes.

578
00:29:33,750 --> 00:29:34,720
We indeed have

579
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:35,780
already done that.

580
00:29:37,270 --> 00:29:38,070
But that

581
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:39,000
doesn't mean

582
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:40,060
I have to marry him.

583
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:41,720
This is too hasty.

584
00:29:42,590 --> 00:29:44,320
When I usually go to pick a shop,

585
00:29:44,440 --> 00:29:46,240
I even scout the location a few times.

586
00:29:46,240 --> 00:29:48,350
Let alone this is a lifelong matter.

587
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:51,790
Besides,

588
00:29:52,350 --> 00:29:53,510
he merely said

589
00:29:53,550 --> 00:29:55,000
he knew what I was worried about,

590
00:29:55,000 --> 00:29:57,060
and agreed to figure out a way with me.

591
00:29:57,270 --> 00:29:59,030
He didn't say he would propose.

592
00:29:59,895 --> 00:30:04,895
(Watch on www.kisskh.xyz Support Admin)

593
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:02,650
Don't laugh.

594
00:30:09,310 --> 00:30:10,350
You mentioned earlier

595
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:12,010
that Uncle Ping sent a letter?

596
00:30:12,160 --> 00:30:14,290
Yes, it just arrived in the afternoon.

597
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:30,360
There is a drought in Pingyang Prefecture.

598
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:32,310
Fetch paper and a brush.

599
00:30:32,310 --> 00:30:33,910
I want to reply to the letter.

600
00:30:36,470 --> 00:30:38,790
[Shan]

601
00:30:42,190 --> 00:30:44,600
[Drought in Shanxi]

602
00:30:49,370 --> 00:30:52,430
[Gu]

603
00:30:52,650 --> 00:30:53,590
What did you say?

604
00:30:55,090 --> 00:30:57,090
Zhao and Chen

605
00:30:57,710 --> 00:30:59,250
are having an affair?

606
00:31:02,310 --> 00:31:03,920
Could you have seen it wrong?

607
00:31:04,590 --> 00:31:05,720
How could I?

608
00:31:06,030 --> 00:31:07,330
I saw her with my own eyes

609
00:31:07,330 --> 00:31:08,470
coming out

610
00:31:08,490 --> 00:31:09,400
of Lord Chen's room.

611
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,330
So late at night,

612
00:31:10,590 --> 00:31:11,750
acting all sneaky.

613
00:31:11,920 --> 00:31:14,180
If that's not a secret affair, what is it?

614
00:31:14,510 --> 00:31:16,640
Besides, Xiaotang saw it too.

615
00:31:17,030 --> 00:31:18,030
Right, Xiaotang?

616
00:31:21,070 --> 00:31:22,720
I was wondering
why the person eavesdropping last night

617
00:31:22,720 --> 00:31:23,680
couldn't be found.

618
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:24,790
It was her.

619
00:31:26,750 --> 00:31:28,350
No wonder!

620
00:31:28,780 --> 00:31:29,910
Why would he suddenly

621
00:31:29,910 --> 00:31:31,960
come to our mansion for no reason?

622
00:31:32,640 --> 00:31:33,500
I really couldn't have imagined.

623
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:35,160
This Chen, a dignified Grand Secretary,

624
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:37,070
actually took a fancy to Zhao.

625
00:31:38,510 --> 00:31:39,510
That's not right.

626
00:31:41,550 --> 00:31:43,070
With Chen's status,

627
00:31:43,400 --> 00:31:44,350
he naturally

628
00:31:44,350 --> 00:31:47,480
would want to marry a noble lady
from a prominent family.

629
00:31:49,790 --> 00:31:51,620
He had a first wife before.

630
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:53,620
This is a second marriage.

631
00:31:54,960 --> 00:31:57,030
Zhao is also a suitable match.

632
00:31:59,590 --> 00:32:00,790
It's still not right.

633
00:32:01,440 --> 00:32:02,880
By acting so secretly,

634
00:32:03,550 --> 00:32:04,400
it's obvious

635
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:05,440
he doesn't want Zhao

636
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:07,240
to have a formal, public status.

637
00:32:07,310 --> 00:32:08,970
If not formalized publicly,

638
00:32:11,720 --> 00:32:12,520
wouldn't Zhao

639
00:32:12,640 --> 00:32:14,510
just become a mistress?

640
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:15,920
Hilarious.

641
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:17,880
What are you laughing at?

642
00:32:18,400 --> 00:32:20,400
If she becomes someone's mistress,

643
00:32:20,590 --> 00:32:23,120
wouldn't that drag down
your reputation too?

644
00:32:24,030 --> 00:32:24,830
Mother,

645
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:28,070
even if this Chen is a Grand Secretary,

646
00:32:28,070 --> 00:32:29,000
a daughter of our Gu family

647
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:30,640
cannot be his mistress!

648
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:31,750
Not to mention

649
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:33,920
Lian's reputation being affected,

650
00:32:33,920 --> 00:32:35,580
our Lord in the imperial court

651
00:32:35,750 --> 00:32:37,790
would completely lose all dignity.

652
00:32:37,790 --> 00:32:38,850
Alright, alright.

653
00:32:39,880 --> 00:32:40,750
This matter

654
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:43,130
must absolutely not be spread.

655
00:32:43,510 --> 00:32:45,510
Not even a single word can be leaked.

656
00:32:45,720 --> 00:32:46,310
Furthermore, you cannot

657
00:32:46,310 --> 00:32:47,880
mention it in front of Zhao.

658
00:32:48,830 --> 00:32:50,550
Why, Grandmother?

659
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:52,160
Haven't you always

660
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:53,820
wanted to teach Zhao a lesson?

661
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:55,460
This is a great opportunity.

662
00:32:55,460 --> 00:32:56,550
What do you know?

663
00:32:56,880 --> 00:32:57,640
What I fear

664
00:32:58,030 --> 00:32:59,110
is not Zhao.

665
00:32:59,550 --> 00:33:01,590
What I fear is Chen.

666
00:33:05,070 --> 00:33:06,130
Listen carefully,

667
00:33:06,310 --> 00:33:07,970
don't cause trouble outside.

668
00:33:08,400 --> 00:33:11,600
Be careful not to bring a great disaster
upon your father.

669
00:33:18,120 --> 00:33:18,790
With such great difficulty,

670
00:33:18,790 --> 00:33:20,550
we caught Gu Jinzhao's weakness,

671
00:33:20,550 --> 00:33:21,110
yet Grandmother actually

672
00:33:21,110 --> 00:33:22,550
forbids me from exposing her.

673
00:33:22,550 --> 00:33:24,080
This is simply outrageous!

674
00:33:29,550 --> 00:33:31,830
Won't let me expose her?

675
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:36,480
Xiaotang.

676
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:37,550
My Lady.

677
00:33:38,350 --> 00:33:40,070
Go find a crowded place,

678
00:33:40,510 --> 00:33:42,680
and spread this matter.

679
00:33:46,350 --> 00:33:47,880
But didn't the Old Madam say

680
00:33:48,000 --> 00:33:50,200
we are forbidden from mentioning this?

681
00:33:51,400 --> 00:33:52,750
I didn't tell you to spread the news about

682
00:33:52,750 --> 00:33:54,680
Gu Jinzhao and Chen Yanyun.

683
00:33:54,920 --> 00:33:56,780
You can just swap in someone else!

684
00:33:56,830 --> 00:33:57,310
Right.

685
00:33:57,310 --> 00:33:58,370
Do you understand?

686
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:07,240
As long as Gu Jinzhao's
reputation is ruined,

687
00:34:07,240 --> 00:34:08,100
perhaps

688
00:34:08,130 --> 00:34:09,860
Chen won't want her anymore.

689
00:34:10,030 --> 00:34:11,110
And the Ji family won't

690
00:34:11,110 --> 00:34:13,110
hand over so many properties to her.

691
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:15,320
When that happens,

692
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:16,650
I'll see what she can do!

693
00:34:23,510 --> 00:34:24,310
Third Master.

694
00:34:26,320 --> 00:34:27,690
Of course it's fake.

695
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:28,880
How could Zhao possibly

696
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:30,630
have an affair with Wang Zan?

697
00:34:33,230 --> 00:34:34,440
Besides, at the Spring Outing,

698
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,030
she was always

699
00:34:35,030 --> 00:34:36,710
with Qinglan and me the whole time.

700
00:34:36,710 --> 00:34:38,630
She didn't even
say a single word to Wang Zan.

701
00:34:38,630 --> 00:34:39,670
But the rumors are told

702
00:34:39,670 --> 00:34:41,510
so convincingly.

703
00:34:42,150 --> 00:34:44,610
They even said Wang Zan
went to the Gu family.

704
00:34:45,190 --> 00:34:48,320
Not only did they exchange
tokens of affection in private,

705
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:50,719
he even stayed overnight
at the Gu mansion.

706
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:53,070
Mother, that sounds
like a rumor right away!

707
00:34:53,070 --> 00:34:54,710
How could you take it seriously?

708
00:34:54,710 --> 00:34:56,960
I hope it's a rumor too.

709
00:34:57,050 --> 00:35:01,060
[Orchid Chamber Fragrance]

710
00:35:00,630 --> 00:35:01,320
Yanyun.

711
00:35:05,150 --> 00:35:05,710
Mother.

712
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:07,800
You came back quite early today.

713
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:09,550
I came back to pack some clothes.

714
00:35:09,550 --> 00:35:11,230
These days, I'm afraid every now and then,

715
00:35:11,230 --> 00:35:12,510
I'll have to stay overnight
at Wenyuan Pavilion.

716
00:35:12,510 --> 00:35:13,710
I came to let you know.

717
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:15,070
Why are you so busy?

718
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:16,880
There is a drought in Shanxi.

719
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:18,670
We must prepare for disaster relief.

720
00:35:18,670 --> 00:35:19,630
The peace talks
with the Northern Barbarians

721
00:35:19,630 --> 00:35:21,190
happen to be in Shanxi as well.

722
00:35:21,190 --> 00:35:25,050
The Ministry of War and the Ministry
of Revenue are both in a scramble.

723
00:35:25,110 --> 00:35:25,920
I heard

724
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:27,280
what you were saying earlier.

725
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:28,590
The Ji family has worked
for me for many years,

726
00:35:28,590 --> 00:35:29,790
with utmost loyalty.

727
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:31,150
Old Madam Ji and Mother

728
00:35:31,150 --> 00:35:32,510
are also close childhood friends.

729
00:35:32,510 --> 00:35:33,630
Those things you heard,

730
00:35:33,630 --> 00:35:35,190
words intentionally slandering Miss Gu,

731
00:35:35,190 --> 00:35:36,800
should have been refuted immediately.

732
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:38,730
Why are you helping to spread them?

733
00:35:39,480 --> 00:35:40,960
At that time,

734
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:42,760
I refuted them.

735
00:35:43,320 --> 00:35:44,400
I just came back

736
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:46,260
to chatter with Yanying about it.

737
00:35:47,030 --> 00:35:48,880
It was just a joke.

738
00:35:49,230 --> 00:35:50,710
Why do you get angry?

739
00:35:50,840 --> 00:35:51,710
Better not

740
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:53,640
to make such jokes in the future.

741
00:35:55,190 --> 00:35:56,280
I still have business to attend to.

742
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:57,610
I will take my leave now.

743
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:02,720
Take good care of Mother.

744
00:36:03,190 --> 00:36:03,670
I'm leaving.

745
00:36:03,380 --> 00:36:11,960
[Orchid Chamber Fragrance]

746
00:36:04,230 --> 00:36:04,840
Alright.

747
00:36:08,670 --> 00:36:10,670
He's used to bossing people around,

748
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:12,590
and now he's lecturing me.

749
00:36:13,030 --> 00:36:13,800
Mother.

750
00:36:21,630 --> 00:36:22,430
Third Master,

751
00:36:22,590 --> 00:36:24,190
Wang Zan is just a scoundrel.

752
00:36:24,320 --> 00:36:25,230
I think this rumor

753
00:36:25,230 --> 00:36:26,230
was spread by him.

754
00:36:27,190 --> 00:36:28,190
Not necessarily.

755
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:29,670
Those who could spread

756
00:36:29,670 --> 00:36:31,360
such talk about staying overnight
at the Gu family

757
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:33,160
could only be from the Gu family.

758
00:36:34,760 --> 00:36:36,150
However, for this matter,

759
00:36:36,150 --> 00:36:39,280
the Wang family still needs to
step forward and clarify.

760
00:36:40,190 --> 00:36:40,670
You may

761
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:42,480
give Mr. Jiang a word of instruction.

762
00:36:42,480 --> 00:36:43,590
He will know what to do.

763
00:36:43,590 --> 00:36:44,070
Yes.

764
00:36:46,630 --> 00:36:48,590
Make another trip to the Gu Mansion.

765
00:36:48,590 --> 00:36:50,280
Ask if Miss Gu has any free time.

766
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:50,960
Just say,

767
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:52,930
I want to see her.

768
00:36:53,520 --> 00:36:54,110
Yes.

769
00:36:55,440 --> 00:36:56,240
Wait a minute.

770
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,710
With the rumor spreading like this,

771
00:37:00,710 --> 00:37:02,590
I'm afraid her situation in the Gu family

772
00:37:02,590 --> 00:37:03,590
is getting worse.

773
00:37:05,720 --> 00:37:06,670
Send an invitation to her

774
00:37:06,670 --> 00:37:07,840
under the name of my mother.

775
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:08,360
Later,

776
00:37:08,550 --> 00:37:09,800
just pick her up.

777
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:11,480
Okay.

778
00:37:15,480 --> 00:37:16,140
Never mind.

779
00:37:16,960 --> 00:37:18,620
I'd better tell her in person.

780
00:37:22,950 --> 00:37:26,100
[Ji's Silk and Satin]

781
00:37:27,190 --> 00:37:28,190
The Boss is here.

782
00:37:31,630 --> 00:37:32,800
I heard recently,

783
00:37:32,880 --> 00:37:33,630
-a new batch
-Have you heard

784
00:37:33,630 --> 00:37:34,670
-of Zhuanghua satin has arrived.
-about that scandal?

785
00:37:34,670 --> 00:37:36,630
-I want to take a look.
-Such a young girl,

786
00:37:36,630 --> 00:37:37,960
so indiscreet!

787
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:39,360
Exactly, so indiscreet.

788
00:37:39,360 --> 00:37:40,890
Why is she here at this time?

789
00:37:42,320 --> 00:37:42,880
Boss,

790
00:37:43,000 --> 00:37:43,820
there are many people here.

791
00:37:43,820 --> 00:37:45,000
Why don't you sit in the private room?

792
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:45,820
No need.

793
00:37:46,230 --> 00:37:47,560
I'll take a look myself.

794
00:37:47,630 --> 00:37:48,400
Do your work.

795
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:49,670
No need to attend to me.

796
00:37:49,670 --> 00:37:50,190
Yes.

797
00:37:57,030 --> 00:37:58,710
Is she Gu Jinzhao?

798
00:37:59,030 --> 00:38:00,430
She looks decent enough.

799
00:38:00,440 --> 00:38:01,070
How could she do

800
00:38:01,070 --> 00:38:02,400
such a shameless thing?

801
00:38:03,190 --> 00:38:04,110
Not even engaged yet,

802
00:38:04,110 --> 00:38:05,590
and already having
secret rendezvous with a man.

803
00:38:05,590 --> 00:38:08,070
But you have to see
which family the man is from.

804
00:38:08,070 --> 00:38:09,530
Court of Judicial Review!

805
00:38:09,630 --> 00:38:11,090
A family of the third rank!

806
00:38:11,190 --> 00:38:13,280
No matter how rich Gu Jinzhao is,

807
00:38:13,300 --> 00:38:15,510
she is still climbing the social ladder
by aiming for the Wang family.

808
00:38:15,510 --> 00:38:16,880
So of course she has to use some tricks!

809
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:18,920
It's the family of
Court of Judicial Review?

810
00:38:18,920 --> 00:38:20,000
Is this true?

811
00:38:20,510 --> 00:38:21,670
Of course!

812
00:38:21,710 --> 00:38:23,000
Could my personal maid

813
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:24,110
possibly lie to me?

814
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:25,670
She said she saw them

815
00:38:25,670 --> 00:38:27,320
holding hands and strolling in the garden.

816
00:38:27,320 --> 00:38:29,120
Wang Zan even stayed overnight!

817
00:38:29,760 --> 00:38:30,760
Impossible!

818
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:33,750
Wang Zan admitted it himself!

819
00:38:33,960 --> 00:38:35,920
According to the provisions
of the Great Yan Code,

820
00:38:35,920 --> 00:38:36,860
a rumormonger

821
00:38:37,070 --> 00:38:40,230
gets 100 strokes of the cane
and 3 years of penal servitude.

822
00:38:40,230 --> 00:38:42,190
Those who cause serious consequences,

823
00:38:42,190 --> 00:38:43,400
get 100 strokes of the cane,

824
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:44,920
and exile to three thousand miles away.

825
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:46,110
You all stand here,

826
00:38:46,360 --> 00:38:47,670
making up such rumors about me.

827
00:38:47,670 --> 00:38:48,790
Right now, I am

828
00:38:49,590 --> 00:38:50,990
unable to defend myself,

829
00:38:51,030 --> 00:38:52,230
and my heart is ashen.

830
00:38:52,920 --> 00:38:54,130
I'm thinking that in a while,

831
00:38:54,130 --> 00:38:56,070
I might as well go find a white silk cloth

832
00:38:56,070 --> 00:38:57,280
and hang myself.

833
00:38:58,830 --> 00:39:00,510
Then, as for all of you rumormongers,

834
00:39:00,510 --> 00:39:02,630
should you be exiled,

835
00:39:02,840 --> 00:39:04,110
or beheaded?

836
00:39:04,440 --> 00:39:05,190
Beheaded?

837
00:39:05,330 --> 00:39:05,920
What should we do?

838
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:07,360
Who are you trying to scare?

839
00:39:07,360 --> 00:39:08,220
Looking at you,

840
00:39:08,230 --> 00:39:09,840
you don't look like someone
willing to hang herself.

841
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:10,400
Exactly.

842
00:39:10,730 --> 00:39:11,900
We said it,

843
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:12,550
so what?

844
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:14,000
The people talking
behind your back

845
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:15,400
are more than just the few of us.

846
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:16,550
All the officials' family members
in the city

847
00:39:16,550 --> 00:39:18,010
know your bad reputation.

848
00:39:18,230 --> 00:39:18,880
Besides,

849
00:39:18,880 --> 00:39:20,810
we weren't the first ones to say it.

850
00:39:21,070 --> 00:39:21,840
Wang Zan

851
00:39:21,840 --> 00:39:23,190
admitted it himself!

852
00:39:23,550 --> 00:39:24,150
Across the whole city,

853
00:39:24,150 --> 00:39:25,400
many people heard it.

854
00:39:25,550 --> 00:39:26,990
He is right across the street
at Baiweizhai.

855
00:39:26,990 --> 00:39:28,920
If you have the guts, go talk to him!

856
00:39:33,120 --> 00:39:34,180
What are you doing?

857
00:39:34,190 --> 00:39:36,050
Trying to run away after talking?

858
00:39:39,990 --> 00:39:41,010
Didn't you say

859
00:39:41,040 --> 00:39:42,840
that Wang Zan started the rumor?

860
00:39:43,110 --> 00:39:43,670
Good.

861
00:39:44,670 --> 00:39:46,400
I'm going to find him right now.

862
00:39:46,880 --> 00:39:48,710
Then you're coming with me.

863
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:51,020
And I invite everyone to be a witness.

864
00:39:51,630 --> 00:39:53,380
Now there's a good show to watch!

865
00:39:53,380 --> 00:39:55,180
Let's see if this is really true.

866
00:39:57,360 --> 00:39:59,000
What, you don't dare?

867
00:39:59,190 --> 00:40:00,320
Why wouldn't I dare?

868
00:40:00,550 --> 00:40:01,360
Let's go then.

869
00:40:04,840 --> 00:40:05,510
Miss Gu,

870
00:40:06,070 --> 00:40:06,920
I'm the butler

871
00:40:06,920 --> 00:40:08,380
from Lord Wang's mansion.

872
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:09,800
Our Lord learned that

873
00:40:09,880 --> 00:40:11,030
the young master offended you.

874
00:40:11,030 --> 00:40:12,510
He has work at the office,

875
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:14,000
so he ordered me

876
00:40:14,440 --> 00:40:15,900
to apologize to you, Miss.

877
00:40:16,400 --> 00:40:17,320
Apologize?

878
00:40:17,900 --> 00:40:19,550
Even the Wang family's chief butler came.

879
00:40:19,550 --> 00:40:21,480
-Could it be a rumor?
-I don't need your apology.

880
00:40:21,480 --> 00:40:22,760
I want your young master

881
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:24,110
to come and apologize in person,

882
00:40:24,110 --> 00:40:25,310
clarify it publicly,

883
00:40:25,320 --> 00:40:26,780
and restore my innocence.

884
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:31,240
Young Master!

885
00:40:31,710 --> 00:40:32,480
Wang Zan!

886
00:40:34,800 --> 00:40:35,590
Is this Wang Zan?

887
00:40:35,590 --> 00:40:36,360
What happened to him?

888
00:40:36,360 --> 00:40:36,920
My father

889
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:39,410
also wants me to apologize.

890
00:40:42,760 --> 00:40:43,920
Who exactly

891
00:40:43,920 --> 00:40:45,190
did I mess with?

892
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:51,190
Miss Gu,

893
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:53,110
I was wrong.

894
00:40:53,710 --> 00:40:55,040
I was completely wrong.

895
00:40:55,800 --> 00:40:56,440
Everyone,

896
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:57,630
everyone,

897
00:40:58,760 --> 00:40:59,760
Miss Gu has never had

898
00:40:59,760 --> 00:41:00,760
a secret rendezvous with me.

899
00:41:00,760 --> 00:41:02,850
My proposal was rejected by her.

900
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:04,150
I held a grudge,

901
00:41:04,150 --> 00:41:05,500
and talked nonsense,

902
00:41:05,670 --> 00:41:06,730
spouting rubbish.

903
00:41:07,550 --> 00:41:08,190
Miss Gu,

904
00:41:08,670 --> 00:41:10,000
the rumors in the capital

905
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:12,200
all started because of my wicked mouth.

906
00:41:12,320 --> 00:41:14,580
But now I have fully realized my mistake.

907
00:41:14,960 --> 00:41:15,590
Please,

908
00:41:17,840 --> 00:41:19,120
Miss Gu, forgive me.

909
00:41:19,320 --> 00:41:20,880
To think he'd do such a thing!

910
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:21,730
It's despicable.

911
00:41:21,730 --> 00:41:22,760
Ruining other's reputation!

912
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:23,480
He really deserves a beating.

913
00:41:23,480 --> 00:41:24,940
-Exactly.
-That's right.

914
00:41:55,440 --> 00:41:57,260
Old Madam, Old Madam!

915
00:41:57,480 --> 00:41:58,110
Old Madam!

916
00:42:06,630 --> 00:42:07,430
What's wrong?

917
00:42:14,630 --> 00:42:15,670
Is this true?

918
00:42:15,920 --> 00:42:16,710
It's true!

919
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:17,590
Everyone is saying

920
00:42:17,590 --> 00:42:18,930
Miss Zhao and Mr. Wang

921
00:42:18,960 --> 00:42:20,070
had a secret affair.

922
00:42:20,070 --> 00:42:20,760
They also said

923
00:42:20,760 --> 00:42:22,510
Mr. Wang stayed overnight in our mansion

924
00:42:22,510 --> 00:42:23,320
and Miss Zhao

925
00:42:23,320 --> 00:42:25,580
went to Cuizhu Residence at night alone.

926
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:28,810
They actually said Zhao

927
00:42:29,280 --> 00:42:30,920
went to Cuizhu Residence?

928
00:42:35,630 --> 00:42:36,840
What an evil girl!

929
00:42:38,280 --> 00:42:39,880
Totally ignoring my words!

930
00:42:41,550 --> 00:42:42,710
Call Lian here!

931
00:42:44,110 --> 00:42:45,110
What does this have

932
00:42:45,110 --> 00:42:45,970
to do with Lian?

933
00:42:46,030 --> 00:42:46,830
Could it be...

934
00:42:47,710 --> 00:42:48,840
If not her, who else?

935
00:42:50,510 --> 00:42:51,770
Then did the Yao family

936
00:42:52,030 --> 00:42:53,550
also hear some rumors?

937
00:42:53,920 --> 00:42:55,190
Most likely they know.

938
00:42:56,630 --> 00:42:57,440
Stupid!

939
00:42:58,230 --> 00:42:59,550
Utterly stupid!

940
00:43:00,550 --> 00:43:01,760
Call her over! Go call her!

941
00:43:01,760 --> 00:43:02,360
Yes.

942
00:43:03,670 --> 00:43:04,510
Grandmother,

943
00:43:05,230 --> 00:43:06,070
look at the hairpin

944
00:43:06,070 --> 00:43:07,200
Wenxiu just gave me.

945
00:43:07,280 --> 00:43:08,280
Does it look good?

946
00:43:09,170 --> 00:43:10,830
You've come at the right time.

947
00:43:13,320 --> 00:43:14,190
Grandmother,

948
00:43:14,880 --> 00:43:16,740
why... why are you hitting me?

949
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:18,510
Kneel down! Kneel down!

950
00:43:22,230 --> 00:43:22,630
I...

951
00:43:23,960 --> 00:43:25,360
Who else would I hit but you?

952
00:43:25,360 --> 00:43:27,760
Do you still consider me your grandmother?

953
00:43:28,400 --> 00:43:29,710
How did I instruct you?

954
00:43:30,590 --> 00:43:31,700
You must not talk

955
00:43:31,760 --> 00:43:34,060
about Zhao and Chen outside!

956
00:43:34,320 --> 00:43:35,140
And what did you do?

957
00:43:35,140 --> 00:43:37,310
Playing smart behind my back outside!

958
00:43:39,480 --> 00:43:40,610
I didn't!

959
00:43:40,880 --> 00:43:41,840
It wasn't me who said it!

960
00:43:41,840 --> 00:43:42,700
If not you, who?

961
00:43:43,550 --> 00:43:46,590
Wang stayed overnight at Cuizhu Residence?

962
00:43:47,000 --> 00:43:48,170
Did you think that

963
00:43:48,230 --> 00:43:50,410
by changing Chen Yanyun to Wang Zan,

964
00:43:50,550 --> 00:43:52,550
others wouldn't find out it was you?

965
00:43:53,590 --> 00:43:54,400
Find out?

966
00:43:55,800 --> 00:43:56,850
How could she?

967
00:43:57,760 --> 00:43:59,110
What evidence does she have to prove

968
00:43:59,110 --> 00:44:00,190
that I said it?

969
00:44:00,280 --> 00:44:00,760
You!

970
00:44:05,280 --> 00:44:06,280
Miss Gu,

971
00:44:10,710 --> 00:44:12,920
my master invites you over to talk.

972
00:44:44,510 --> 00:44:45,400
At this hour,

973
00:44:45,400 --> 00:44:47,330
did you just come out of the palace?

974
00:44:49,360 --> 00:44:50,440
I'm about to go in.

975
00:44:51,960 --> 00:44:53,070
Recently,

976
00:44:53,670 --> 00:44:55,800
I may have to rest at Wenyuan Pavilion.

977
00:44:55,880 --> 00:44:57,230
I was a bit worried about you,

978
00:44:57,230 --> 00:44:58,290
so I came to see you.

979
00:45:01,440 --> 00:45:03,510
Did you also hear the rumors?

980
00:45:04,550 --> 00:45:05,750
You've been wronged.

981
00:45:09,000 --> 00:45:10,550
Did Wang Shenzhi

982
00:45:10,670 --> 00:45:12,530
send someone to apologize to you?

983
00:45:12,710 --> 00:45:13,360
Yes.

984
00:45:15,000 --> 00:45:16,030
You arranged it?

985
00:45:18,110 --> 00:45:19,440
How did you manage that?

986
00:45:20,030 --> 00:45:21,030
He is a third-rank

987
00:45:21,030 --> 00:45:22,550
Chief Minister
of the Court of Judicial Review!

988
00:45:22,550 --> 00:45:24,150
I have evidence against him.

989
00:45:24,400 --> 00:45:26,000
In the 29th year of Jingning,

990
00:45:26,070 --> 00:45:27,950
when he was the county magistrate
in Wanping,

991
00:45:27,950 --> 00:45:28,710
at that time,

992
00:45:29,110 --> 00:45:30,570
a wealthy man surnamed Liu

993
00:45:30,880 --> 00:45:31,920
committed a crime.

994
00:45:31,920 --> 00:45:33,480
He was supposed to be exiled,

995
00:45:33,480 --> 00:45:34,630
but Wang Shenzhi

996
00:45:35,070 --> 00:45:36,210
exonerated him,

997
00:45:36,360 --> 00:45:37,840
reducing it to half a year in prison,

998
00:45:37,840 --> 00:45:40,070
and accepted three thousand taels
of silver.

999
00:45:40,070 --> 00:45:41,070
You know all this?

1000
00:45:41,840 --> 00:45:42,880
How did you know?

1001
00:45:43,440 --> 00:45:44,320
Actually,

1002
00:45:45,150 --> 00:45:46,320
I'll tell you later.

1003
00:45:49,070 --> 00:45:50,400
Keeping me in suspense.

1004
00:46:05,130 --> 00:46:08,560
[A Splendid Match]
